<HEADLINE> Graf to Compete in Hamburg Open </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, March 8 (Xinhua) -- Former world number one Steffi Graf
of Germany will play in the Hamburg Open women's tennis tournament
next month, tournament director Guenter Sanders said on Monday.
</P>
<P>
Graf was the winner of the event during the period from 1987-
1991. She never compete in Hamburg again after that. 
</P>
