<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, March 8 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 3,847.44 points on Monday, down 10.66
 points, or 0.28 percent, from Friday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover stood at over 83 trillion Turkish Liras (over
335 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 45.56 points, or 0.70 percent,
to close at 5,045.76 points, the services index fell 23.98
points, or 0.49 percent, to close at 5,058.28 points, while
the industrial index rose 15.21 points, or 0.58 percent, to
close at 2,652.85 points. 
</P>
