There is nothing mystical about writing a constitution" he said.
</P>
<P>
Organizations such as the National Constitutional Assembly
already had their proposed draft constitutions in place.
</P>
<P>
Zvobgo said the good faith of the government lay in its
determination to have all stakeholders represented in the proposed
commission of inquiry.
</P>
<P>
The government's proposal was that the commission to be
appointed by President Robert Mugabe would carry out intensive
research to determine the nature of constitution the people want,
he said.
</P>
