<HEADLINE> Ethiopia Trains 11,400 School Directors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, March 8 (Xinhua) -- The Ministry of Education of
Ethiopia announced on Monday that it has a plan to train 11,000
primary and 400 secondary school directors between June and
September 1999.
</P>
<P>
Vice-Minister of Education Tekle-Hayimanot Haile-Sellassie told
a meeting here that the training will help promote a smooth
teaching-learning process across the country.
</P>
