efforts to become a full member of the Council of Europe.
</P>
<P>
He also praised the contribution of Cyprus' ethnic Armenians
to the progress in Cyprus and the close relations between
Armenian Cypriots and Greek Cypriots.
</P>
<P>
The 2,500 Armenians living in Cyprus island opted to be part of
the Greek Cypriot community when the island gained independence
from the British colonial rule in 1960.
</P>
<P>
Earlier Tuesday, Cyprus President Glafcos Clerides received
Oskanyan.
</P>
<P>
