the seventh plenum of the Sixth Congress of the Lao People's
Revolutionary Party Central Committee, which calls for strongly
boosting agriculture, manufacturing and border trade. He also
stressed the measures to be taken to combat inflation, including
tapping income sources, punishing smugglers, curbing illegal
currency exchange, boosting tourism, more thrift among the general
public, improving the confidence in the local currency kip, and
support for the implementation of the socio-economic development
plan. 
