escaped legal punishment. It noted that bribery cases have
seriously damaged efforts to build a clean and honest government.
</P>
<P>
The circular instructed courts and procuratorates across the
country to attach great importance to the anti-corruption campaign,
with emphasis on seeking punishment for those convicted of
attempted bribery as well as those accepting bribery.
