<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 9 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
March 10, 1999, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station
at 17:00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -2 degrees C., max. 5 degrees C., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. -12 degrees C., max. -2 degrees C., cloudy to
clear, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 1 degree C., max. 6 degrees C., sleet to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 4 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., overcast, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 10 degrees C., max. 14 degrees C., overcast, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chongqing: min. 9 degrees C., max. 12 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Kunming: min. 11 degrees C., max. 25 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Nanjing: min. 2 degrees C., max. 7 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, gentle to moderate breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai: min. 4 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., drizzle, fresh
breeze to strong breeze.
</P>
<P>
Wuhan: min. 4 degrees C., max. 6 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hangzhou: min. 3 degrees C., max. 6 degrees C., drizzle to
moderate rain, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 16 degrees C., max. 20 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 20 degrees C., max. 24 degrees C., overcast,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 19 degrees C., max. 24 degrees C., overcast,
gentle to moderate breeze.  
</P>
