<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, March 9 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
increased 28 HK dollars to close at 2,693 HK dollars a tael today,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 291.75 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, 3.04 U.S. dollars up from the previous close at today's
exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7480 HK dollars.
</P>
</TEXT>
