Shaquille O'Neal, Minnesota Timberwolves forward Kevin Garnett,
New York Knicks center Patrick Ewing, Portland forward Brian Grant,
Sacramento forward Chris Webber, Toronto Rookie swingman Vince
Carter and Washington forward Juwan Howard. 
