Courtney defeated Sergio Vidal 7-6, 6-4, and Chad Valdez and Juan
Pablo Herrera beat Javier Taborga and Jose Antelo 4-6, 7-6, 6-2.
</P>
<P>
The Netherlands Antilles placed fifth, beating Jamaica 2-1.
</P>
<P>
Panama, Bolivia, Netherlands Antilles and Jamaica remain in the
third division, while Honduras and Antigua-Barbuda drop into the
fourth. 
